accessibility.text: Lauren is the owner and Creative Director of Bunny Paige, a Cleveland based jewelry design and mixed media art studio founded in 2013.  She holds degrees in International Business and Marketing from AIU.

Her original and instantly recognizable Spiked Hearts and forward thinking designs have allowed her to grow from local business to a thriving brand with an international cult following. Laurens work has been featured on celebrity clients, the runways of NYFW, and most recently the stage of Cirque Du Soleil.

Laurens brings a passionate energy to this project which stems from her upbringing as the granddaughter of a judge and civil rights lawyer who served as a member of President John F. Kennedy's diplomatic team and legal counsel to Martin Luther King Jr.
Lauren looks forward to continuing in her familys footsteps while helping to build a brighter future for the entire LGBTQ+ community.
